# 🧪 Antidote Mixed

When someone tries to use kill button on you, their cooldown will be decreased by configurable amount of time.

  • Max
    • Set the Maximum amount of Antidote that can be in a match
  • Spawn Chance
    • Set the percentage players have of getting Antidote
  • Impostors can become Antidote
    • ON: Impostors can become this role
    • OFF: Impostors cannot become this role
  • Crewmates can become Antidote
    • ON: Crewmates can become this role
    • OFF: Crewmates cannot become this role
  • Neutrals can become Antidote
    • ON: Neutrals can become this role
    • OFF: Neutrals cannot become this role
  • Decrease the cooldown by
    • Set how much the cooldown will be decreased by
  • Cooldown returns to normal after a meeting
    • ON: Killer's cooldown will return to normal after a meeting
    • OFF: Killer's cooldown will not return to normal after a meeting
